title: 252: Instant Wild-Card Round Preview
itunes:title: 252: Instant Wild-Card Round Preview
description:
As the regular season comes to a close, Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks react to the Wild-Card matchups and take a quick dive into each game (1:28) . Bucky then gives his 5 takeaways after seeing the finalized Top 10 NFL Draft order (18:54). Will Jon Gruden fit in Oakland if he does in fact return? DJ and Bucky have the answer (26:15).
